    <item>
      <title>随着关税动荡的蔓延，全球市场崩溃加深了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/global-market-meltdown-deepens-as-trump-holds-firm-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税释放的金融市场上的屠杀持续不断，因为股票遭受重创，而美国股票期货表明上周的5万亿美元废除还没有结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/global-market-meltdown-deepens-as-trump-holds-firm-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 05:38:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国讨论加速刺激以应对特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-discusses-frontloading-stimulus-to-counter-tariff-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉的人说，中国的决策者讨论了周末的措施，以稳定经济和市场，面对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税袭击，包括是否加速计划以释放刺激刺激以增强消费量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-discusses-frontloading-stimulus-to-counter-tariff-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 05:19:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易敏感的澳大利亚资产下降了关税的烦恼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/trade-sensitive-australian-assets-drop-as-risk-sentiment-spirals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚依靠贸易的资产扩大了崩溃，投资者继续权衡唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税，因为总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯表示，他的政府将继续与美国互动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/trade-sensitive-australian-assets-drop-as-risk-sentiment-spirals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 02:15:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密特朗普的集会随着关税野蛮风险资产而蒸发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/bitcoin-btc-plunges-into-asia-open-as-crypto-feels-trade-war-pain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在11月初选举赢得胜利以来，加密货币几乎消除了他们的所有收益，因为美国总统的关税袭击的后果引发了他发誓要参加冠军的资产类别的沉重销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/bitcoin-btc-plunges-into-asia-open-as-crypto-feels-trade-war-pain</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 00:37:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股票对关税的“恐慌”投降；国防部股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/european-stock-futures-drop-after-worst-week-since-march-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股票下降，在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税公告后面下降到自2023年12月以来的最低水平，德国的DAX指数下降了10％。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/european-stock-futures-drop-after-worst-week-since-march-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 00:29:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票溃败恶化，债券在关税动荡上集会：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球股票的踩踏者聚集了势头，投资者堆积在避风港资产中，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税加深了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国呼吁平静，新鲜计划应对特朗普的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/china-floats-rate-cuts-industry-aid-to-counter-trump-tariff-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税加息，中国警告不要恐慌，称其有足够的政策室来捍卫经济，但不排除与美国进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/china-floats-rate-cuts-industry-aid-to-counter-trump-tariff-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本的尼克基（Nikkei）进入熊市，而Ishiba寻求关税协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/japanese-stocks-set-to-tumble-as-trade-war-fears-intensify</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本的Nikkei 225股票的平均水平滑入了熊市市场，担心贸易战正在扩大，而政府则试图达成一项广泛的协议，以与华盛顿以美国关税进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/japanese-stocks-set-to-tumble-as-trade-war-fears-intensify</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:09:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
